02/24/2021,748.363(4) - Reports and Record Keeping,Reports and Record Keeping,No,03/10/2021,02/25/2021,D:Reports and Record Keeping,Medium,No,Two staff files reviewed did not contain high school diplomas. ,"The administrator e-mailed me a copy of both staff members high school diplomas and stated she would be sure to put a copy of the staff members high school diplomas, college diploma, or school transcript in all staff files in the future."
